video_info.title: Day 21: 15 MIN FULL BODY STRETCH - Perfect for your Rest Day (HIIT IT HARD - The Comeback Challenge)
video_info.description:
A full body stretch that is perfect for your rest day or as a morning routine to feel more flexible! Press play and follow along. Give your body this 15 minutes, stretch and recover - ready for your next active day! Enjoy

♡ Sign up to my Grow with Anna APP: https://growwithanna.com?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=launch

▸ Level: All Levels
▸ Time: 15 Min
▸ Equipment: No Equipment

Please remember that we are all different and that you can make this your own workout ♡ Take a longer break when you need to.
